===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Caitlin (Masters)}}
Caitlin forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Reuniclus}} and {{p|Sableye}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Her Sableye is capable of [[Mega Evolution|Mega Evolving]]. Caitlin became a playable sync pair on October 31, 2019.

Caitlin has also made notable appearances in one of the game's main stories, the [[PML arc]].

